{"tid":628600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柯P看AIT新館心得 「美國就是美國」","createTime":"2018-04-14T04:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T21:07:15.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1f7e4b50f98499f2b301da33633c9d1345527af2","tid":628600,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T04:28:36.000Z","msg":"柯P看AIT新館心得 「美國就是美國」<br />\n<br />\n美國在台協會AIT內湖新館即將完成，處長梅健華（Kin Moy）昨天在臉書上說，很高興能歡迎台北市長柯文哲到AIT內湖新館參觀，柯是「第一位台灣的VIP訪客」。今天柯文哲被問到參訪的感想，認為「反正美國就是美國」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">AIT內湖新館目前還沒有全部完工，但昨日已經邀請柯文哲前去參觀。柯文哲說，這棟新館造價70幾億，是台北市重要的建築，可見台灣對美國來講還是很重要的地方，才願意花70幾億去蓋一個大使館。<br />\n<br />\n柯說，去看看新館，領略一下美國文化，他得知全美國在世界各地的大使館，包括動線什麼的，都以SOP的標準流程在蓋，「反正美國就是美國」。</span><br />\n<br />\n媒體問柯，是否感到很驚艷，柯說，這是花70幾億蓋的，且70幾億是看得到的，至於沒有看到的國防預算是多少，就不曉得了。<span style=\"color: red;\">至於比蔡英文總統更早前往參觀，有覺得備受禮遇嗎？柯說「沒有啦，通常是小的先去。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7323/3085183\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7323%2F3085183&d=WxIVqh6e2MKgQ83lfIU2XEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=7d6704e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7323/3085183</a>"},{"pid":"c4551a2013cc5175aff805115c428c7b56974f14","tid":628600,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T04:31:00.000Z","msg":"好想知台北市民點評價呢位市長"},{"pid":"7bde84f86ad6955de8114ae08996be2096a03304","tid":628600,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T04:31:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc60d1e8c217b2f9078530a37ca7fdca23b80d78","tid":628600,"uid":53672,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"70幾億就收爹啦，我地幾千億都未敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715667a2be8a3895e8f3517cbce1ff3e127e5f8b","tid":628600,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T04:33:30.000Z","msg":"原來係台幣添"},{"pid":"969d90f471feccec8d031bc0e3aa6ccdc90c727b","tid":628600,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7dbe540e6667af14babcdf64cfa3bc17569190","tid":628600,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"沒有啦，通常是小的先去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又幾得意"},{"pid":"1ef8a567b34ff9ac78fa4fa01ca21a995cd325c8","tid":628600,"uid":56624,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7bde84f86ad6955de8114ae08996be2096a03304","tid":628600,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T04:31:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T18:56:07.000Z","msg":"你連特首都冇得選，邊有資格批評台北選民，關你鬼事？"},{"pid":"e06c7e30a257e0cee83815c2639cd8d50cccf651","tid":628600,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c4551a2013cc5175aff805115c428c7b56974f14","tid":628600,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T04:31:00.000Z","msg":"好想知台北市民點評價呢位市長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:17:11.000Z","msg":"反正低B就是低B<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fb53dba1a3691f1f6f78952ef199d10c0060f6","tid":628600,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:44:35.000Z","msg":"同香港又有幾分相似<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/mike4444/1321157973-3199810297.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fmike4444%2F1321157973-3199810297.jpg&h=928dd4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20131003/large/03we10pt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.